{"tid":1457044,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Android 版Airdrop：Files by Google","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T07:51:53.000Z","uid":130698,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d103dc92dd2a8f4de94a5744959fdf9f1657f773","tid":1457044,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"Android 既朋友 download 定files，offline 傳送資料<br />\n萬一冇網絡都可以透過Bluetooth wifi 黎傳送訊息，雖然佢冇背景開啟嘅功能，都不失為一個發佈訊息嘅途徑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.nbu.files\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.google.android.apps.nbu.files&d=5%2F0N1eX%2FnGDFGLWAFE16zgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=06bdfcf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.nbu.files</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOkkUhd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOkkUhd.jpg&h=e33e5a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新手安裝流程：</span><br />\n首先使用WhatsApp 或Instagram製圖或影相，預備好素材就按分享<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp  製圖：於對話中按相機制，隨意拍照，按右上角畫筆制，在空白位長按兩秒。按右邊的顏色條轉色，再按Ｔ右上角第二，隨意打字或者畫畫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ha9NzmB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHa9NzmB.jpg&h=de7ad68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzMszmH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzMszmH.jpg&h=be7453c7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n－<br />\n－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">初次設定   選擇儲存於sd卡內</span><br />\n首先開啟Files 程式，然後允許程式權限：地點，儲存空間。然後到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>設定</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DuHLk2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDuHLk2d.jpg&h=3d2cf011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etBHofW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetBHofW.png&h=bab5c759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返回主頁面按右下角分享，然後按中間位置嘅傳送或接收。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Judq5yb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJudq5yb.png&h=489a1f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我得一部電話，所以做唔到之後嘅示範。主要都係按照佢嘅指示選擇確認/同意/允許，就可以傳送圖片/文件。另外，佢冇背景開啟嘅功能，所以要開5-10 mins 先會收到資料。<br />\n<br />\n希望呢啲資料幫到各位朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老手安裝流程：</span><br />\n設定－－＞選擇儲存於sd卡內<br />\n完成晒初次設定，可以按圖片--&gt; 分享--&gt; 透過Files 應用程式傳送。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qJyuXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qJyuXX.jpg&h=e5790690&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"205405855ba6a194d09cb759963889d22e112996","tid":1457044,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58572444918d436f0926b3d4d0ac5f591de77749","tid":1457044,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1976afa07a7fae43be33993f7cb10f36eb239aa","tid":1457044,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f59c99d2eccbe875389e94eb31c77170e242c1f","tid":1457044,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4673820bfe309c0370e6d8340c788128c24fa73c","tid":1457044,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdeaaf240949bd03b18dfb460af8d0e51ab0ee0e","tid":1457044,"uid":